A:/> C:
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Filesystem Error Handling Test
C:/> 
C:/> # Tests that the filesystem reports errors correctly and
C:/> 
C:/> # remains in a consistent state after each error.
C:/> 
C:/> #
C:/> 
C:/> # Exercises:
C:/> 
C:/> #   - RF on non-existent file
C:/> 
C:/> #   - RD on non-empty directory
C:/> 
C:/> #   - CD to non-existent directory
C:/> 
C:/> #   - Create duplicate file (CF to existing name)
C:/> 
C:/> #   - NF (rename) to existing name
C:/> 
C:/> #   - CF to non-existent subdirectory path
C:/> 
C:/> #   - MD duplicate directory
C:/> 
C:/> #   - SUM of non-existent file
C:/> 
C:/> #   - RF on a directory (should fail)
C:/> 
C:/> #   - RD on a file (should fail)
C:/> 
C:/> #   - Filesystem remains consistent after all errors
C:/> 
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 1: Remove non-existent file
C:/> 
C:/> RF NOSUCHFILE.TXT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 2: CD to non-existent directory
C:/> 
C:/> CD NOSUCHDIR
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 3: Create a test directory with a file for further tests
C:/> 
C:/> MD TESTDIR
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT TESTDIR/FILE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 4: RD on non-empty directory
C:/> 
C:/> RD TESTDIR
Error: Directory not empty.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 5: Create duplicate file (CF where dest already exists)
C:/> 
C:/> # This should succeed (CF overwrites by design)
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT DUPE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT DUPE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> SUM DUPE.TXT
1382 1
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 6: NF (rename) to existing name
C:/> 
C:/> NF DUPE.TXT SCOTT.TXT
Error: Already exists.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 7: CF to path with non-existent intermediate directory
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT FAKEDIR/FILE.TXT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 8: MD duplicate directory
C:/> 
C:/> MD TESTDIR
Error: Already exists.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 9: SUM of non-existent file
C:/> 
C:/> SUM GHOST.TXT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 10: RF on a directory (not a file)
C:/> 
C:/> RF TESTDIR
Error: Not a file.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 11: RD on a file (not a directory)
C:/> 
C:/> RD DUPE.TXT
Error: Not a directory.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 12: LF non-existent file
C:/> 
C:/> LF MISSING.TXT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 13: CD to a file (not a directory)
C:/> 
C:/> CD DUPE.TXT
Error: Invalid parameter.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 14: NF (rename) non-existent source
C:/> 
C:/> NF PHANTOM.TXT NEWNAME.TXT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 15: MD in non-existent parent
C:/> 
C:/> MD FAKEDIR/SUBDIR
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 16: Verify filesystem is still consistent
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
 <DIR> TESTDIR
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
    15 DUPE.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 17: Verify files are still accessible after all the errors
C:/> 
C:/> SUM DUPE.TXT
1382 1
C:/> 
C:/> SUM TESTDIR/FILE.TXT
1382 1
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 18: Clean up
C:/> 
C:/> RF DUPE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF TESTDIR/FILE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RD TESTDIR
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
C:/> 
